data.description: This beautiful Hill country home sits on a corner lot in the desirable Woods of Boerne subdivision.  It has 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths, large living room, eat in kitchen and separate dining room. In the beautiful kitchen, you'll find a large breakfast bar, island and walk in pantry in an open-concept with full access between the living room and dining area. Woods floors are in abundance throughout the first floor. The master suite boasts separate his and hers walk in closets, oversized shower and separate garden tub and separated vanities. The fourth bedroom, family room and bath are conveniently located upstairs and is perfect for a teenager or guests. The over sized backyard has a large covered patio.
